thread.title: Tammy
thread.title_full: White Mountain Puzzles reviewed by Tammy

author: Tammy
title: Tammy
text: I have many of the collage puzzles and I love the size, the design and everything about them. Unfortunately, I received a Washington state puzzle for a present and it was poorly cut. A ton of puzzle dust and hard to put together because of the bad cut. I was able to complete it and the only puzzle I ever had like that. I still rate these five star because they deserve it.
